      "author": "GS-AX",
      "description": "## What's New in 0.3.0\n\n- **Fetch Page by URL** - Import any Confluence page instantly by pasting its URL; optionally pull in direct children or the entire subtree (BFS)\n- **Image download** - Attached images are saved to `_attachments/{pageId}/` in your Vault and embedded locally so they work offline\n- **4 languages** - UI and notices available in English, ???, ???, ????\n- **Wiki-link toggle** - Convert Confluence internal page links to Obsidian `[[wiki-link]]` format (optional)\n- **Jira Weaver bridge** - Automatically replace bare Confluence URLs in Jira Weaver notes with `[[wiki-links]]`\n- **Custom field mappings** - Map any dot-path in the Confluence page JSON to a custom frontmatter key\n- **Korean / Unicode filenames** - File names now preserve Korean and other Unicode characters correctly\n- **requestUrl migration** - All HTTP calls use Obsidian's `requestUrl` API, fixing connection issues in Electron\n\n## Assets\n\n| File | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `main.js` | Compiled plugin bundle |\n| `manifest.json` | Plugin metadata |\n| `styles.css` | Plugin styles |",
